{
  "texts": [
    "We analyzed databases from multiple SMEs across various industries, focusing on turnover in a general context rather than in relation to a specific firm. 2.",
    "We suppose that there is a deficiency in the literature regarding the analysis of datasets with more than a thousand variables.",
    "A multilayer network approach significantly increases the amount of information considered in the feature engineering step.",
    "The multilayer network approach to organisations provides an opportunity to further refine and characterize network actors such as the quality of relationships of seekers or brokers. 3.",
    "A self-developed data-driven approach was used to select the most influential factors, taking into account the combined predictive power of the variables. 4."
  ]
}